    "Requires University SSO login (email @kampus-non-merdeka.ac.id). Receives a subsidised fare (Rp3,000) and payment options using E-Toll Card or QRIS. Maximum of 4 seats per transaction.": "Requires University SSO login (email @kampus-non-merdeka.ac.id). Receives a subsidised fare (Rp3,000) and payment options using E-Toll Card or QRIS. Maximum of 4 seats per transaction.",
